ackground:#BDB76B;\" | [[BAFTA Award for Best Actress in a Supporting Role|Best Actress in a Supporting Role]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n''' [[Clive Owen]] \u2013 ''[[Closer (2004 film)|Closer]]'' '''\n* [[Alan Alda]] \u2013 ''[[The Aviator (2004 film)|The Aviator]]''\n* [[Phil Davis (actor)|Philip Davis]] \u2013 ''[[Vera Drake]]''\n* [[Jamie Foxx]] \u2013 ''[[Collateral (film)|Collateral]]''\n* [[Rodrigo de la Serna]] \u2013 ''[[The Motorcycle Diaries (film)|The Motorcycle Diaries (Diarios de motocicleta)]]''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n''' [[Cate Blanchett]] \u2013 ''[[The Aviator (2004 film)|The Aviator]]'' '''\n* [[Julie Christie]] \u2013 ''[[Finding Neverland (film)|Finding Neverland]]''\n* [[Heather Craney]] \u2013 ''[[Vera Drake]]''\n* [[Natalie Portman]] \u2013 ''[[Closer (2004 film)|Closer]]''\n* [[Meryl Streep]] \u2013 ''[[The Manchurian Candidate (2004 film)|The Manchurian Candidate]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#BDB76B;\" | [[BAFTA Award for Best Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]]\n! style=\"background:#BDB76B;\" | [[BAFTA Award for Best Adapted Screenplay|Best Adapted Screenplay]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n''' ''[[Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind]]'' \u2013 [[Charlie Kaufman]]'''\n* ''[[The Aviator (2004 film)|The Aviator]]'' \u2013 [[John Logan (writer)|John Logan]]\n* ''[[Collateral (film)|Collateral]]'' \u2013 [[Stuart Beattie]]\n* ''[[Ray (film)|Ray]]'' \u2013 [[James L. White]]\n* ''[[Vera Drake]]'' \u2013 [[Mike Leigh]]\n| valign=\"top\" |\n''' ''[[Sideways]]'' \u2013 [[Alexander Payne]] and [[Jim Taylor (writer)|Jim Taylor]]'''\n* ''[[The Chorus (2004 film)|The Chorus (Les choristes)]]'' \u2013 [[Christophe Barratier]] and Philippe Lopes-Curval\n* ''[[Closer (2004 film)|Closer]]'' \u2013 [[Patrick Marber]]\n* ''[[Finding Neverland (film)|Finding Neverland]]'' \u2013 [[David Magee]]\n* ''[[The Motorcycle Diaries (film)|The Motorcycle Diaries (Diarios de motocicleta)]]'' \u2013 [[Jos\u00e9 Rivera (playwright)|Jos\u00e9 Rivera]]\n|-\n! style